recommended_degree: Ilmu Komputer, Teknik Informatika, Teknik Elektro, Statistika dan Sains Data, Matematika (Sarjana)
job_description:
- Data Annotation: Labeling images and videos for training our vision models (bounding boxes, segmentation, classification) 
- Model Testing: Running experiments, testing model performance, documenting results 
- Quality Checking: Reviewing model outputs, identifying edge cases and failure modes 
- Building & Experimentation: Contributing to building pipelines, trying new approaches, and improving existing systems 
- Documentation: Maintaining clear records of datasets, experiments, and findings
